Version 2.8.31                                                      2011-09-11
==============================================================================

0.    KNOWN ISSUES

      CR20019836
      State-Aware Proxy
      
      BasicState state instances returned by a container based iterator must 
      not be updated while the iteration is in progress.

      CR20019584
