		Specification-Version: 3.4.1
		Specification-Vendor: ICU
		Implementation-Title: ICU for Java
		Implementation-Version: 3.4.1
		Implementation-Vendor: IBM Corporation
		Implementation-Vendor-Id: com.ibm      
      
