      * correctly in case of UTC
      * incorrectly for a lot of other time zones 

      The problem was detected under the following conditions
      * org::w3c::dateTime value < 1970-01-01T00:00:00.000Z 
      * SQL type TIMESTAMP WITH TIMEZONE 
                  
